<div class="container">
  <div class="about-section" >
    <h1>About This Application</h1>
    <p>PantryPal is a recipe sharing platform allows users to create, explore and filter through recipes.</p>
    
    <ul>
      <li>Share your own recipes with the community</li>
      <li>Browse recipes created by other users</li>
      <li>Filter meals by preperation time</li>
      <li>Find recipes that suit your dietry needs</li>
      <li>Stay on budget by sorting recipes estimated by cost </li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>This project was built for educational purposes.</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="tech-stack">
    <h2>Technology Stack</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js, Express.js</li>
      <li><strong>Database:</strong> MongoDB with Mongoose ODM</li>
      <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> HTML, CSS, JavaScript (Vanilla)</li>
      <li><strong>Template Engine:</strong> EJS</li>
      <li><strong>Authentication:</strong> bcrypt, express-session</li>
      <li><strong>Security:</strong> csurf for CSRF protection</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

